Chase the Lady, Chapter 9: Jaeger calls out Rachel for her behavior.
The Once and Future Mr. Monster, Chapter 3: Max Zero gloats over defeating Mr. Monster.

The Once and Future Tarzan, Chapter 6: The ship hits rough water.
